defaultstudy it can be inferred that accelerating train relative to the cyclist is an occupational hazard. Because in a relative (from Albert Einstein’s perspective) universe, inertial path is greater than accelerated path or in geometric terms, the diagonal of a
default triangle is more than sum of it sides is shown by Sir Roger Penrose
default 
default(Penrose, 2004)
default. These findings are counter –intuitive to 
defaultancient Greek (Pythagoras theorem) and 17
defaultth
default Century (Newtonian dynamics) physics
